---
title: Hearty Bison and Black Bean Chili with Mexican-Spiced Sweet Potato
description: We're giving chili night an upgrade so that you can spend more time watching the game! Tonight’s chili is full of Mexican-seasoned sweet potato, smoky meat and hearty beans. A dollop of sour cream and a sprinkle of cheese finishes each bowl with a fresh and creamy touch.
